{"tid":519992,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[猜謎語] 發現一隻值博率好高嘅美股","createTime":"2018-01-05T02:57:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-12T10:47:17.000Z","uid":125976,"like":3,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"aec7fb26a91279f1af53ed84d1a8b415d5998272","tid":519992,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T02:57:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/05/105346_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F05%2F105346_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=6c007f49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n謎面：<br />\n小明家境清貧，老豆係裝修佬。<br />\n<br />\n老豆見小明想學鋼琴，就用咗幾塊裝條剩嘅瓷磚整咗個鐵片琴畀小明玩。小明攞起兩隻食指彈，彈得幾過癮。<br />\n<br />\n當然小明返到學校同佢啲同學仔分享，佢啲同學個個有學琴，笑佢戇撚鳩死窮鬼。<br />\n<br />\n小明自此發奮圖強，大個做咗 IT 狗，寫咗隻 Game，好受師奶歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n猜一美股。<br />\n<br />\n利申：有貨，仲有得升。<br />\n<br />\n求求大家，估中都唔好開估<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"183f815aad8aa131dc1cf89eb570a93a33c0eeb3","tid":519992,"uid":125976,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T03:21:58.000Z","msg":"送錢都冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"074928e2e6cae540a65c605431e52a826d8e49a4","tid":519992,"uid":20908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T03:24:22.000Z","msg":"未買過股票<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c853c39fff21aeefb96aa6366289e55e17a7e0f","tid":519992,"uid":7615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T03:32:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94c78699d8655aa3c11573ff9616a7852ae9c270","tid":519992,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T01:54:42.000Z","msg":"今日回咗少少，有錢可以加注<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <b